Romero Jennings, MAC’s Director of Makeup Artistry, is inspiring; at 60, his energy is infectious and his passion about his art is intriguing. For someone who has spent over three decades in the industry, his thoughts and opinions about men embracing makeup are insightful to say the least. Head to the link in bio to know what he has to say about the changing scenario of beauty across the world, men breaking stereotypes and how empowering the idea of self-care is.
